 face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Please also understand that the company is obligated to keep the account current per the terms and conditions of the Agreement.&nbsp; Any credit due will be granted at the resolution of the claim.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif">While in most instances it may take significantly less time,&nbsp;<b style=""><span style="background: yellow;">please allow us up to 90 days to resolve your claim</span></b>. &nbsp;We will contact you if additional information is required.</font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="">Regards,</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Lucida Calligraphy&quot;; color: rgb(64, 64, 64);">Fleet Fraud Services</span><p class="MsoNormal" style=""><span style="color: rgb(64, 64, 64);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="" size="2">Fax: 207-791-1655</font></span></p></div><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></font>]]></td>
